ActFinancial Administration Act
SubjectTwo Ontario Ferry Operators Remission Order
PrecisWill provide for the remission of the fees that are payable by Bluewater Ferry Inc. and Walpole-Algonac Ferry Line Ltd., which operate in the St. Clair River in Ontario, for icebreaking services provided by the Canadian Coast Guard in the period beginning on April 1, 2001 and ending on May 15, 2009 under the Icebreaking Services Fee Schedule made under subsection 47(1) of the Oceans Act, as well as a portion of the fees that are payable for those services in subsequent years.
RegistrationRegistration: SI/ 2009-0054 Publication Date: 2009-06-24
AttachmentsAttachment
